1124
01:18:15,579 --> 01:18:16,579
[SPEAKER_02] Uho mu.

1125
01:18:16,579 --> 01:18:18,579
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, ozdravio sam ga odmar.

1126
01:18:18,579 --> 01:18:19,579
[SPEAKER_02] Di s tima?

1127
01:18:19,579 --> 01:18:20,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, Isus nije tako.

1128
01:18:20,579 --> 01:18:21,579
[SPEAKER_02] Mi možda je...

1129
01:18:21,579 --> 01:18:22,579
[SPEAKER_02] Isus nije tako.

1130
01:18:22,579 --> 01:18:23,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubiš nije.

1131
01:18:23,579 --> 01:18:24,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ok.

1132
01:18:24,579 --> 01:18:26,579
[SPEAKER_02] Praćuje se, to je naš Bog.

1133
01:18:26,579 --> 01:18:29,579
[SPEAKER_02] I Marija...

1134
01:18:29,579 --> 01:18:31,579
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, je samo ti.

1135
01:18:31,579 --> 01:18:33,579
[SPEAKER_02] Nas vodi njegov.

1136
01:18:33,579 --> 01:18:35,579
[SPEAKER_02] Zato onaj ga, jer ja vjerujem da ga vješam.

1137
01:18:35,579 --> 01:18:36,579
[SPEAKER_02] Evo.

1138
01:18:36,579 --> 01:18:37,579
[SPEAKER_02] Evo.

1139
01:18:37,579 --> 01:18:38,579
[SPEAKER_02] Evo.

1140
01:18:38,579 --> 01:18:40,579
[SPEAKER_02] E može jedan vic nekakar?

1141
01:18:40,579 --> 01:18:41,579
[SPEAKER_02] Može.

1142
01:18:41,579 --> 01:18:43,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ajma jedan vic, malo da.

1143
01:18:43,579 --> 01:18:53,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ljudi nas pitaju, onda mi re, koja je razlika među Isusovci, Saluzijance, frate, kurvi, pater, dor, frate, ovo, ono, rač.

1144
01:18:53,579 --> 01:18:58,579
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ja ću vam reći jednu sliku, pa vi, evo ga, kažu zajedno se molim predijanima.

1145
01:18:58,579 --> 01:19:00,579
[SPEAKER_02] A prijatno vam ša se slupio.

1146
01:19:00,579 --> 01:19:01,579
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan Isovac.

1147
01:19:01,579 --> 01:19:02,579
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan Domenikanac.

1148
01:19:02,579 --> 01:19:03,579
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan frater.

1149
01:19:03,579 --> 01:19:04,579
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan benedetinac.

1150
01:19:04,579 --> 01:19:05,579
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan Saluzijanac.

1151
01:19:05,579 --> 01:19:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] Mole zajedno.

1152
01:19:06,579 --> 01:19:07,579
[SPEAKER_02] To su psalmi, evo?

1153
01:19:07,579 --> 01:19:09,579
[SPEAKER_02] I pukne žaroljak.

1154
01:19:09,579 --> 01:19:11,579
[SPEAKER_02] I...

1155
01:19:11,579 --> 01:19:12,579
[SPEAKER_02] Brak.

1156
01:19:12,579 --> 01:19:13,579
[SPEAKER_02] I sad petorica.

1157
01:19:13,579 --> 01:19:16,579
[SPEAKER_02] Svaka reakcija ukazuje na karizmu.

1158
01:19:16,579 --> 01:19:17,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ok, frater, zaspol.

1159
01:19:17,579 --> 01:19:20,579
[SPEAKER_02] Frater odmah zaspol.

1160
01:19:20,579 --> 01:19:25,579
[SPEAKER_02] Benedetinac, on šiba, on zna psalme na pamet.

1161
01:19:25,579 --> 01:19:26,579
[SPEAKER_02] On moli na pamet.

1162
01:19:26,579 --> 01:19:27,579
[SPEAKER_02] On ide dalje.

1163
01:19:27,579 --> 01:19:30,579
[SPEAKER_02] Isusovac ne zna napred, ali on tumači ono što ovaj moli.

1164
01:19:30,579 --> 01:19:32,579
[SPEAKER_02] Zna, tumači psalme.

1165
01:19:32,579 --> 01:19:35,579
[SPEAKER_02] A Domenikanac pobija njegovo tumačenje.

1166
01:19:35,579 --> 01:19:40,579
[SPEAKER_02] A Saluzijanac promijenio žarolju.

1167
01:19:40,579 --> 01:19:44,579
[SPEAKER_02] Promijenio žarolju.

1168
01:19:44,579 --> 01:19:48,579
[SPEAKER_02] To je mala slika, karizmu.

1169
01:19:48,579 --> 01:19:50,579
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala vam lijepa.

1170
01:19:50,579 --> 01:19:51,579
[SPEAKER_02] Bogaš blagosloge.

1171
01:19:51,579 --> 01:19:52,579
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala vam.

1172
01:19:56,579 --> 01:19:58,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ja se odmah ne skričavam.

1173
01:19:58,579 --> 01:19:59,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sutra imam...

1174
01:19:59,579 --> 01:20:00,579
[SPEAKER_02] Kad me Paterike pitao...

1175
01:20:00,579 --> 01:20:01,579
[SPEAKER_02] Već sam imao u kalendaru.

1176
01:20:01,579 --> 01:20:05,579
[SPEAKER_02] Sutra imam cijelojdenu duhovnogodnu za moju montavnu zajednicu Božju pobjedu.

1177
01:20:05,579 --> 01:20:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da to je cijelina sutra.

1178
01:20:06,579 --> 01:20:08,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam moram večera se radati u Zagrebu.

1179
01:20:08,579 --> 01:20:13,579
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da ja odmah nakona govora Moravić pa vas sve pozažava mi je što ne mogu ostati ovdje.

1180
01:20:13,579 --> 01:20:19,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ali evo, hvala Patriku na pozivu, na povjerenju i svima bali što ste došli za ovoga.

1181
01:20:25,579 --> 01:20:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] Na srce se zahvaljujem Odan Daniela Stojiću na ovom prekrasnom, zanimljivom i inspirativnom govoru.

1182
01:20:32,579 --> 01:20:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem svatko od nas mogo pronaći nešto za sebe i nešto što ćemo pohraniti u srce i dalje prebirati.

1183
01:20:39,579 --> 01:20:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tako nam približiti Božju ljubav i evo u ovom govoru o strahotama Pavla, o očistilištu, ali i o neizrecivim ljepotama raja.

1184
01:20:52,579 --> 01:20:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem da smo pronašli nešto što može još produbiti našu občežnju za nebo.

1185
01:20:57,579 --> 01:21:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo još jednom srcu hvala Damiru.

1186
01:21:00,579 --> 01:21:13,579
[SPEAKER_03] Usikaj ćemo svako da se vidi, Damir, i vi ostavite tu gdje jeste i možete mahnuti.

1187
01:21:13,579 --> 01:21:15,579
[SPEAKER_03] Neko da znači usika.

1188
01:21:15,579 --> 01:21:17,579
[SPEAKER_03] Ko ima?

1189
01:21:17,579 --> 01:21:19,579
[SPEAKER_03] Ajde.

1190
01:21:19,579 --> 01:21:49,560
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala što pratite kanal.

1191
01:21:49,579 --> 01:22:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala što pratite kanal.

